    "body": "You can do it from the the main process this way:\n\n```\nvar exec = require('child_process').exec\nexec(process.argv.join(' ')) // execute the command that was used to run the app\napp.quit() // quit the current app\n```\n\nEdit: then to make it work from the html page, either use the `remote` module or the `ipc` modules.\nAlso, see issue https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/539 \n"
