    "body": "It seems the app is terminated before being restarted; the only thing I can think of now is to wrap the last line in a setTimeout function to ensure the command has had enough time to be executed before killing the app:\n\n```\nvar exec = require('child_process').exec\nexec(process.argv.join(' ')) // execute the command that was used to run the app\nsetTimeout(function(){\n  app.quit()\n},50) // wait 50ms before killing the app\n```\n"
